articles.title: Standoff at Dutch nightclub ends with hostages freed, suspect in custody - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Police said there was no indication of a ‘terrorist motive’ after four people were held in the town of Ede.
articles.content:
An hours-long standoff at a nightclub in the central Netherlands has ended with the release of all the hostages and a suspect in custody, Dutch police said.
The last hostage has just been released. … [+2939 chars]
